Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.20,0:39:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样被插上了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.35,0:40:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服, 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.01,0:40:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.82,0:41:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因为米亚很漂亮\N所以想给你满满的疼爱
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.62,0:41:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,主人...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.58,0:41:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.14,0:41:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好像又要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.49,0:41:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.60,0:41:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好像要去了, 好像要去了...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.08,0:41:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,主人, 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.34,0:42:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.71,0:42:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,火腿肠的味道怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.26,0:42:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我的最爱
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.99,0:42:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,味道啊,刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.45,0:42:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了, 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.12,0:42:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.39,0:42:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,每天都会努力服务.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.25,0:42:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我也在公司里
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.91,0:42:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,努力工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.82,0:42:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.23,0:42:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚也很高兴, 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.98,0:43:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.35,0:43:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.55,0:43:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,可以舔一舔
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.43,0:44:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.17,0:44:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,刺激我一下吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.12,0:44:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了, 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.39,0:45:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这个西兰花也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.10,0:45:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.83,0:46:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.82,0:46:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.03,0:46:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,再看一下龟头
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.74,0:46:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,会有满满的液体飞出来
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.52,0:47:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.34,0:47:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,深深的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.25,0:47:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,可以放进去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.14,0:47:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,手放开
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.30,0:48:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,再舔一舔
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.44,0:48:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚舔的我很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.18,0:49:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,眼里看不见饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.51,0:49:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴, 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.75,0:49:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚, 感觉很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.87,0:50:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,再激烈一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.24,0:50:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.60,0:52:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.47,0:52:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,又要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.91,0:52:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,可以射在你脸上吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.29,0:52:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.67,0:52:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,请把米亚的脸射的满满的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.64,0:53:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好像要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.10,0:53:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,要出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.71,0:53:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,主人的精液非常温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.98,0:53:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可以帮我清理一下吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.09,0:53:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可以哦 帮您清理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.65,0:54:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,主人, 全部都射出来了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.30,0:54:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,能努力工作吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.96,0:54:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,工作
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.07,0:54:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我可以非常努力地做到这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.57,0:54:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.58,0:54:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.43,0:54:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了, 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.99,0:54:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,给你这个, 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.79,0:55:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你, 米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.85,0:55:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.33,0:55:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以亲你再出去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.65,0:55:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.72,0:55:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想去上班了。
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.64,0:55:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那样不行哦, 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.58,0:55:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.16,0:55:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.57,0:55:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一路走好, 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.48,0:56:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,主人来电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.03,0:56:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是, 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.28,0:56:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.66,0:56:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,现在在忙吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.76,0:56:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是, 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.86,0:56:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好像把重要的文件放在桌子上了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.64,0:56:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,看得见吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.77,0:56:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.62,0:56:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了, 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.54,0:56:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚, 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.31,0:56:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你能把它带到公司吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.52,0:56:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了, 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.14,0:56:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,活过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.87,0:57:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.45,0:57:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.58,0:57:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心。
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.86,0:57:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是, 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.24,0:57:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.33,0:57:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,又能见到主人了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.39,0:57:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,蟾蜍社长
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.02,0:57:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这次真的非常感谢你\N-不用, 不用
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.31,0:57:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们公司也签订了合同
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.21,0:57:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这可能是一种双赢的关系。
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.59,0:57:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你这么说。
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.45,0:57:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,进军亚洲真的辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.59,0:57:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,出乎意料的难\N我们也很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.93,0:57:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.66,0:57:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这并不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.75,0:57:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎样，单在国内是有点吃力的。
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.19,0:57:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,都是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.45,0:57:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哪位?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.42,0:57:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,主人?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.25,0:57:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,进来吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.87,0:58:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,女佣?\N-对
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.26,0:58:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.15,0:58:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,主人, 我把文件拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.95,0:58:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚, 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.17,0:58:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这个对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.00,0:58:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对了,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.43,0:58:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,托你的福活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.94,0:58:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,啊,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.64,0:58:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.81,0:58:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们家的女佣
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.49,0:58:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面。
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.08,0:58:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱\N-是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.97,0:58:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,社长真的没关系吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.89,0:58:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了。
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.80,0:58:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,蟾蜍和社长
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.62,0:58:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,今后也长久地
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.55,0:58:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,维持关系。
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.19,0:58:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.37,0:58:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.19,0:58:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,吉村可夫的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.99,0:58:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,吉村(蟾蜍)社长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.50,0:58:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,吉村康夫和我们公司
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.70,0:58:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,以后会合作事业
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.17,0:58:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,计划进军亚洲
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.96,0:59:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,吉村社长对于我们公司
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.58,0:59:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是十分贵重的人
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.33,0:59:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.69,0:59:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是, 主人...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.86,0:59:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.03,0:59:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,送给吉村社长了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.86,0:59:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你表现得可爱点
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.79,0:59:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.16,0:59:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.94,0:59:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 你可以留在这里。
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.40,0:59:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 社长
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.33,0:59:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,下次再联系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.33,0:59:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.06,0:59:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是叫米亚酱吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.18,0:59:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.48,0:59:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.24,0:59:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,个子是多少?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.72,0:59:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,145
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.58,1:00:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,145?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.85,1:00:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.33,1:00:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的喜好的类型
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.06,1:00:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 到这边来
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.00,1:00:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,来这里。
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.21,1:00:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.84,1:00:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.17,1:00:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么可推辞的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.92,1:00:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.00,1:00:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.88,1:00:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你, 不是听社长说了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.22,1:00:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,真的没事吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.94,1:00:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,现在就走的话
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.88,1:00:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,端中社长的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.59,1:00:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,脸会被你抹黑
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.90,1:00:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算让主人为难吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.56,1:00:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不好吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.64,1:00:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,按照我说的做
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.45,1:00:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不会让你痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.58,1:00:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,真是我喜欢的类型呢
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.18,1:01:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心。
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.62,1:01:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会做坏事的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.38,1:01:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.88,1:01:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,请到这边来\N-请不要这样
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.15,1:01:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.57,1:01:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.72,1:01:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,脸转过来看我
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.11,1:01:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要这样，吉村大人\N-已经这样了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.31,1:01:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要这样，吉村大人\N-过来
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.40,1:01:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.07,1:01:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,吉村大人，不要这样做。
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.71,1:01:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要这样
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.33,1:01:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要这样\N-别费劲
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.28,1:01:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,下面很紧呢
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.20,1:01:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好\N-不要
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.53,1:01:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢插进去
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.62,1:01:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我插进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.82,1:02:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,很紧我非常喜欢。
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.63,1:02:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,放松一下
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.44,1:02:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,都已经这么淋湿了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.29,1:02:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,吉村,请不要这样......
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.27,1:02:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微动一下
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.27,1:02:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越深入了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.30,1:02:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,太紧了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.98,1:02:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,想要我更深地进去吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.47,1:03:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要这样。
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.81,1:03:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.03,1:03:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我的东西
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.92,1:03:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我要深入顶到你的心
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.91,1:03:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真是一张可爱的脸蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.79,1:03:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.26,1:03:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要这样
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.25,1:03:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.46,1:03:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你想接吻吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.45,1:03:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好好伸出舌头来看看
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.23,1:04:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了，年轻的女孩
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.60,1:04:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,骑上
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.30,1:04:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,更深入
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.68,1:04:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,主人...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.41,1:04:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,再..
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.59,1:04:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不讨厌吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.99,1:04:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,深入到深处，
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.31,1:04:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不是很舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.62,1:04:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.33,1:04:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这个我也要品尝
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.78,1:04:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.90,1:04:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.58,1:04:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.98,1:05:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,变得滑溜溜了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.56,1:05:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.08,1:05:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还差得远呢。
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.31,1:05:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这次转过来
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.09,1:05:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,往这边
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.62,1:05:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股伸过来
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.66,1:06:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不挺好,我就要惩罚你了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.91,1:06:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.76,1:06:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,主人们...\N-好了 靠近我点
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.62,1:06:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真下流
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.52,1:06:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.39,1:06:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,主人...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.79,1:06:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.91,1:06:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,请帮帮我, 主人...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.31,1:06:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.40,1:06:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.41,1:06:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,全都进去了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.12,1:06:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,主人...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.52,1:06:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你不喜欢里面被插满吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.98,1:06:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.54,1:07:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,再伸过来点
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.57,1:07:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,主人...\N-看到很清楚嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.02,1:07:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,主人, 请帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.50,1:07:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了，这小屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.07,1:07:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,进去得挺深啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.58,1:07:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,请别这样
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.74,1:07:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,请别这样
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.00,1:07:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.39,1:08:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.84,1:08:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,到这边来。
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.30,1:08:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,舔一下
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.86,1:08:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,插进过你的小穴的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.41,1:08:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,继续舔
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.47,1:09:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是的。
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.10,1:09:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好好舔一下
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.17,1:09:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,舔的再深一点
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.37,1:09:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,够到了我会告诉你
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.82,1:09:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,把它插进你的喉咙深处
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.28,1:10:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,自己好好舔
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.22,1:10:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那样的,是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.71,1:10:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不是告诉你了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.62,1:10:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴收紧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.83,1:10:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这次给我好好做
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.89,1:10:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不一样嘛,再深一点啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.48,1:10:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,含到喉咙里
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.52,1:10:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,认真点
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.14,1:11:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.62,1:11:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不能好好做
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.26,1:11:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我会取消和Hatanaca社长的合作！
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.26,1:11:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这样还吗!?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.20,1:11:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你才合作失败!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.15,1:11:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以好好的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.88,1:11:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,按照我说的做我说
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.09,1:11:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.36,1:11:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出你的舌头
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.82,1:11:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,把舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.68,1:11:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,再伸出来多点
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.52,1:12:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真下流
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.39,1:12:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒啊。
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.51,1:12:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好喜欢, 我要舔遍你下流的全身
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.50,1:12:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,皮肤真好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.89,1:12:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这个应该很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.30,1:12:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好大的胸部啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.58,1:12:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这么大的吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.89,1:13:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这边有感觉吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.88,1:13:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你都已经湿了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.35,1:13:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,只用手指插进去了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.73,1:13:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴张开
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.10,1:13:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,口水好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.84,1:13:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,很美味
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.57,1:13:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个好女孩
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.57,1:13:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.47,1:14:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,坐在沙发上
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.53,1:14:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,坐在沙发上
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.79,1:14:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样抓着你的腿
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.73,1:14:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,求我帮你舔
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.86,1:14:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,请帮我舔一下...\N-很好
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.60,1:14:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.53,1:14:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真美味
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.17,1:14:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,说请尽情的舔我的小穴
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.47,1:14:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,说请尽情的舔我的小穴
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.41,1:15:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,请尽情的舔我的小穴...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.39,1:15:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好喜欢
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.22,1:15:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我硬起来了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.40,1:15:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,保持这个姿势
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.09,1:15:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这样用手指插入
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.72,1:15:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样? 这样舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.40,1:16:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真是下流的小穴啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.47,1:16:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,流出来好多水呢
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.31,1:16:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃。
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.90,1:16:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我要再次插进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.87,1:17:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好宝地啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.79,1:17:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,啊,太紧了...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.00,1:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真是最棒的小穴 好紧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.17,1:17:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我的肉棒插的你舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.84,1:17:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.25,1:17:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,再给你点
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.53,1:17:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.71,1:18:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,夹得好紧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.65,1:18:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好喜欢
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.82,1:18:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,到这边来。
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.00,1:18:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,往这边
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.87,1:18:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,自己动
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.43,1:18:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,把我的肉棒放进你的小穴里
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.11,1:18:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,让我可以看到
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.40,1:18:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看不见啊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.87,1:18:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.98,1:18:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,自己动动看
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.52,1:18:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好厉害的小穴
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.15,1:19:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,让我再舒服点
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.83,1:19:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,说请我好好感受你的小穴
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.84,1:19:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,请好好感受我的小穴...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.89,1:19:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,再动一动
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.07,1:20:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不要随便给我去了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.54,1:20:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.32,1:20:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,到这边来
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.85,1:20:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股靠过来
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.75,1:20:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,下流的小屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.77,1:20:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,非常滑溜呢
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.51,1:20:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.37,1:20:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.38,1:20:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,吸的好紧啊好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.84,1:20:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.78,1:20:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这样打你的小屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.01,1:21:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,有感觉吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.08,1:21:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我会更深入的插入
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.03,1:21:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,把双手放在我的膝盖上
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.44,1:21:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样才能插的更深
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.30,1:21:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,脚丫
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.02,1:22:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好喜欢
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.18,1:22:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这样舔你怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.80,1:22:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 真是美味
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.59,1:22:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来脱了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.04,1:22:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很好
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.30,1:22:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,摇晃你的腰部
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.51,1:22:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,再摇一摇
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.03,1:23:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,也给我看看你的胸部
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.29,1:23:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,把腿张开点
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.80,1:23:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.98,1:23:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,抽插
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.03,1:24:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,爽死人了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.71,1:24:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,再动快点
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.31,1:24:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.96,1:24:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,抽插这里舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.37,1:24:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,主人, 对不起...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.85,1:25:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚, 好像又要去了\N对不起...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.95,1:25:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你的小穴都舒服的这么湿了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.27,1:25:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这样好吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.46,1:25:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你丢了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.13,1:25:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可爱的女孩
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.77,1:25:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,躺着
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.14,1:26:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好像又要去了...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.67,1:26:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,主人...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.35,1:26:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,主人, 对不起...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.40,1:26:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了, 要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.67,1:26:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那么怎么不道歉
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.46,1:26:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,主人...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.48,1:26:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.30,1:26:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.92,1:26:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,发出这么淫荡的声音
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.32,1:27:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉高潮了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.89,1:27:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那样 舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.41,1:27:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒要进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.84,1:27:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要肉棒吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.27,1:27:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.13,1:28:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,到这边来
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.89,1:28:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,还差得远呢。
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.50,1:28:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.97,1:28:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有那么舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.56,1:28:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是这个情况吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.61,1:29:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好像要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.24,1:29:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把你射的满满的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.83,1:29:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.67,1:29:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,说是\N-是
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.35,1:29:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,说请把我射的满满的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.00,1:29:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,请把我射的满满的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.99,1:29:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在这可爱的脸上
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.35,1:29:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,射得满满的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.31,1:30:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.87,1:30:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,又拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.04,1:31:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了。
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.04,1:31:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了。
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.13,1:31:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,什么呀,不是在吗
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.65,1:31:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.60,1:31:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.51,1:32:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.02,1:32:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.86,1:32:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.30,1:32:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.86,1:32:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.58,1:32:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.47,1:32:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,您是怎么想的?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.33,1:32:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.94,1:32:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就算交给别人
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.50,1:32:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你也觉得无所谓吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.70,1:33:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚是主人的
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.66,1:33:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚只有主人
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.69,1:33:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.65,1:33:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.21,1:33:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚心里不开心
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.31,1:33:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.85,1:34:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,再给我一次机会
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.01,1:34:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不会做今天这样的事了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.05,1:34:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,像傻瓜一样的我
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.68,1:34:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你能原谅我吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.71,1:34:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,主人...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.10,1:34:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.20,1:35:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.50,1:35:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,作为和好的纪念
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.87,1:35:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要一起
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.71,1:35:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,洗漱吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.51,1:35:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.83,1:35:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你的是说洗澡吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.93,1:35:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.74,1:36:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.02,1:36:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那个小袋子里是什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.23,1:36:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这个吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.78,1:36:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.24,1:36:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,今天对米亚的事
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.24,1:36:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我错了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.74,1:36:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这是礼物
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.00,1:36:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么呀?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.39,1:36:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不行。
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.63,1:36:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不可以看\N 等一会
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.71,1:36:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,快进去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.54,1:36:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,领带 失礼了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.70,1:36:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,衬衫也失礼了。
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.01,1:37:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,裤子也失礼了。
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.98,1:38:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,内衣也失礼了。
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.33,1:39:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.07,1:39:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.98,1:39:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在的味道不臭吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.36,1:39:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一点也不臭哦,主人
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.03,1:39:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还是有点不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.11,1:41:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,吸的深一点吧
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.22,1:42:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.14,1:42:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,进去吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.47,1:42:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好的, 主人
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.24,1:42:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我放在这里
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.56,1:42:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.48,1:42:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我来服侍您洗澡
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.92,1:43:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.91,1:43:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,再靠近点
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.42,1:44:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那么请帮我洗一下肉棒吧?\N-是
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.98,1:44:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.47,1:44:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可以把手再深入点哦
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.00,1:45:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.00,1:45:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,现在变干净了吗?\N-是
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.60,1:45:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,身体也会帮你洗
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.92,1:46:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.03,1:46:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,都洗好了吗?\N-是
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.76,1:46:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.61,1:47:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那么这次
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.43,1:47:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我来给米亚洗澡
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.29,1:47:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,站着
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.62,1:47:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,该洗哪里呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.01,1:48:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不行...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.23,1:48:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这里可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.55,1:48:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 帮你弄干净
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.61,1:48:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,胳肢窝也要洗干净
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.31,1:48:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,把手抬高
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.33,1:48:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,再站直一点
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.25,1:48:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,要听话哦
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.07,1:48:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要洗干净哦
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.85,1:49:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头变硬了很下流哦
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.80,1:49:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服, 主人
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.26,1:49:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这边也给你洗一下
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.93,1:49:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这边
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.26,1:49:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这里该洗了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.73,1:50:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你有好好洗这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.05,1:50:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,它很干净
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.73,1:50:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但还是
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.10,1:50:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有地方要洗啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.51,1:50:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那么这次
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.09,1:50:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,里面你也洗得干干净净吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.49,1:50:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,主人, 什么啊? 那个
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.27,1:50:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.42,1:50:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.52,1:50:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是里面用的
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.83,1:50:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,洗刷工具啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.62,1:50:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.89,1:50:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你用力，它就会掉的
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.81,1:51:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这样旋转可以把里面洗干净
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.83,1:51:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我给你买的礼物
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.00,1:51:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.83,1:51:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,仍然还要再洗洗呢
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.68,1:51:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那就这样做吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:04.80,1:52:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,再回头看看吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.31,1:52:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得里面都洗干净了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.49,1:52:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,里面也变干净了...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.27,1:52:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.19,1:52:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,再干净一点吧
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.20,1:53:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.66,1:53:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.56,1:53:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.47,1:53:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.65,1:53:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那样跳起来的话,这个会断的哦
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.21,1:53:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,主人 真是的...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.26,1:53:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那用水冲洗干净吧
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.51,1:54:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这样胳肢窝没法洗呀
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.71,1:54:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好好抬起来
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.20,1:54:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,腋下无法洗掉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.89,1:55:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,变得干净了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.09,1:55:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.15,1:55:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那么进浴池吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.05,1:55:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,比平时更美丽的胸部啊
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.49,1:55:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,看了好想舔呢
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.74,1:56:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚小姐的身材什么时候看都很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.34,1:56:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.04,1:56:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.68,1:56:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是帮你身体洁净的工具
Dialogue: 0,1:57:04.91,1:57:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,看看
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.86,1:57:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,震动的这么厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,1:57:50.98,1:57:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,试着骑在我身上
Dialogue: 0,1:58:22.56,1:58:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,再用力一点吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.40,1:58:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服, 主人
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.26,1:58:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,再看看
Dialogue: 0,1:59:08.25,1:59:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要再调高档位?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:25.50,1:59:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.03,1:59:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚, 好像又要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.63,1:59:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以去吗??
Dialogue: 0,1:59:38.66,1:59:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好像要去了, 好像要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:24.57,2:00:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚真的很可爱
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.29,2:00:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,2:00:44.14,2:00:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这次可以让美亚为主人服务吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:58.46,2:01:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,2:01:26.59,2:01:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可以舔一舔哦,乳头
Dialogue: 0,2:01:57.88,2:01:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里可以看到
Dialogue: 0,2:01:59.72,2:02:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,最好的屁股
Dialogue: 0,2:03:23.26,2:03:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,因为米亚的服务
Dialogue: 0,2:03:26.88,2:03:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,一下子就勃起了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:03:30.23,2:03:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以吮吸你的肉棒吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.50,2:03:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,2:05:24.45,2:05:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只可以用嘴吸吮
Dialogue: 0,2:05:27.48,2:05:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,手放开
Dialogue: 0,2:06:35.29,2:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,2:06:37.55,2:06:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,差点儿射了
Dialogue: 0,2:07:52.85,2:07:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,2:07:54.59,2:07:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好喜欢
Dialogue: 0,2:07:58.49,2:08:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这里也是
Dialogue: 0,2:08:04.80,2:08:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以用它擦胸部哦
Dialogue: 0,2:08:07.75,2:08:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,用主人的肉棒擦胸部好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:09:23.83,2:09:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,舔我的乳头
Dialogue: 0,2:10:00.85,2:10:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头和肉棒都很舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:29.70,2:11:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,2:11:30.86,2:11:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,请满满的射给我
Dialogue: 0,2:11:50.09,2:11:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:12:50.78,2:12:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,2:12:51.87,2:12:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,2:13:04.34,2:13:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好像要射了
Dialogue: 0,2:13:41.31,2:13:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,2:13:43.34,2:13:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,射出来了这么多
Dialogue: 0,2:13:48.28,2:13:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我会帮您舔干净的
Dialogue: 0,2:14:34.56,2:14:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,2:14:36.23,2:14:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,水温怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:39.47,2:14:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,2:14:41.61,2:14:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那我去为您准备晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,2:16:21.57,2:16:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,睡着了啊
Dialogue: 0,2:21:05.58,2:21:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,主人,不行
Dialogue: 0,2:21:07.56,2:21:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好像又要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:21:11.25,2:21:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,2:21:16.51,2:21:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好像要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:21:18.33,2:21:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了, 要去了...
Dialogue: 0,2:21:35.08,2:21:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,2:21:37.82,2:21:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,2:21:41.01,2:21:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,今天
Dialogue: 0,2:21:42.62,2:21:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,因为今天是玩游戏的日子\N※旁白 : [名词]过去, 男人晚上偷偷潜入恋人的寝室的事情.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:44.57,2:21:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你得假装睡着了\N※旁白 : [名词]过去, 男人晚上偷偷潜入恋人的寝室的事情
Dialogue: 0,2:21:49.30,2:21:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,2:21:50.84,2:21:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起, 主人
Dialogue: 0,2:21:56.99,2:21:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,重新开始
Dialogue: 0,2:21:59.00,2:22:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,2:22:05.12,2:22:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你要装作好好睡觉
Dialogue: 0,2:22:06.86,2:22:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,2:28:37.93,2:28:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,2:28:40.65,2:28:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了\N好像又要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:28:47.94,2:28:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,2:28:48.91,2:28:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好像又要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:29:31.91,2:29:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚真敏感呢
Dialogue: 0,2:29:38.45,2:29:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起, 主人...
Dialogue: 0,2:29:44.54,2:29:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,2:29:51.15,2:29:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢这一点
Dialogue: 0,2:30:23.37,2:30:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好孩子
Dialogue: 0,2:31:03.80,2:31:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴好滑溜都湿哒哒了
Dialogue: 0,2:31:06.79,2:31:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:31:12.30,2:31:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,让我再多看看
Dialogue: 0,2:32:45.64,2:32:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,内裤现在不需要了吧?
Dialogue: 0,2:34:49.24,2:34:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好像又要去了...
Dialogue: 0,2:34:56.49,2:34:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好像要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:34:58.51,2:34:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好像要去了, 好像要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:37:12.57,2:37:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,流了很多汗
Dialogue: 0,2:37:44.97,2:37:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,摸摸我
Dialogue: 0,2:41:05.63,2:41:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:41:07.73,2:41:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我好好舔一下蛋蛋
Dialogue: 0,2:41:10.35,2:41:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,2:42:51.53,2:42:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,2:42:55.16,2:42:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒
Dialogue: 0,2:42:57.15,2:42:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可以放进去吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:43:01.49,2:43:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,2:43:04.55,2:43:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,2:43:52.65,2:43:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,找到那个舒服的地方
Dialogue: 0,2:44:29.35,2:44:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服...
Dialogue: 0,2:44:32.46,2:44:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很开心
Dialogue: 0,2:45:46.94,2:45:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,2:45:48.80,2:45:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好极了...
Dialogue: 0,2:45:50.86,2:45:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,主人...
Dialogue: 0,2:45:54.86,2:45:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,让我再看看你的脸
Dialogue: 0,2:46:23.00,2:46:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好像又要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:46:24.81,2:46:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好像又要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:46:25.86,2:46:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了, 要去了...
Dialogue: 0,2:46:40.82,2:46:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,又丢了...
Dialogue: 0,2:46:43.50,2:46:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,2:46:48.13,2:46:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这次让我看看屁股
Dialogue: 0,2:46:53.00,2:46:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要就这样拔出来
Dialogue: 0,2:48:04.71,2:48:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚, 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,2:48:07.57,2:48:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了,我动不了了...
Dialogue: 0,2:48:13.01,2:48:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,塞得满满的全都进去了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:48:39.78,2:48:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:48:41.55,2:48:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:49:11.83,2:49:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了, 要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:49:13.54,2:49:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:49:15.44,2:49:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好像又要去了...
Dialogue: 0,2:49:31.32,2:49:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股靠过来
Dialogue: 0,2:50:39.38,2:50:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,主人, 真的太好了...
Dialogue: 0,2:51:16.96,2:51:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚真的很敏感
Dialogue: 0,2:51:21.20,2:51:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我要用肉棒把你插更深
Dialogue: 0,2:51:59.64,2:52:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴里面好舒服...\N-舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,2:52:27.57,2:52:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,到这边来
Dialogue: 0,2:54:20.04,2:54:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,比平时更敏感啊
Dialogue: 0,2:54:23.21,2:54:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,抱着我抓紧
Dialogue: 0,2:56:56.53,2:56:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真的太好了..
Dialogue: 0,2:57:32.83,2:57:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好像要射了
Dialogue: 0,2:57:36.33,2:57:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,再
Dialogue: 0,2:57:37.68,2:57:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可以射在你脸上吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:57:41.03,2:57:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可以哦, 主人
Dialogue: 0,2:57:43.36,2:57:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在美亚的脸上
Dialogue: 0,2:57:45.29,2:57:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,请全部射出来射得满满的
Dialogue: 0,2:59:18.63,2:59:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,2:59:22.24,2:59:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,2:59:26.05,2:59:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是, 主人
Dialogue: 0,2:59:30.91,2:59:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好好睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,2:59:54.14,2:59:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,各位,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,2:59:57.17,3:00:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这次是第一次担任制造的角色
Dialogue: 0,3:00:03.39,3:00:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,很紧张
Dialogue: 0,3:00:05.89,3:00:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,很努力了
Dialogue: 0,3:00:08.35,3:00:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不介意的话
Dialogue: 0,3:00:09.40,3:00:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,3:00:12.38,3:00:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,今后
Dialogue: 0,3:00:13.41,3:00:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我会努力做到更熟练
Dialogue: 0,3:00:17.00,3:00:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,请多多关照七沢米亚
Dialogue: 0,3:00:20.92,3:00:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那我去叫醒主人了
Dialogue: 0,3:00:27.16,3:00:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,主人?
Dialogue: 0,3:00:29.03,3:00:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,（附赠）
Dialogue: 0,3:00:31.75,3:00:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次试穿女仆的衣服。
Dialogue: 0,3:00:35.21,3:00:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,3:00:39.06,3:00:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好紧张啊,我会努力尝试的
Dialogue: 0,3:00:42.96,3:00:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 十分抱歉, 读错了台词...
Dialogue: 0,3:00:46.73,3:00:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,主人, 现在是早上
Dialogue: 0,3:00:50.61,3:00:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,(笑场了...)
Dialogue: 0,3:00:54.80,3:00:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我好害羞。
Dialogue: 0,3:00:58.61,3:01:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我感到惭愧，因为我的对手没有反应\N-我很惭愧......
Dialogue: 0,3:01:01.66,3:01:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,3:01:03.14,3:01:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那个袋子里是什么?
Dialogue: 0,3:01:05.90,3:01:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这个?
Dialogue: 0,3:01:07.26,3:01:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不是告诉过你叫科福罗(小袋子)吗...
Dialogue: 0,3:01:11.99,3:01:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,只要按照指示去做
Dialogue: 0,3:01:14.29,3:01:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不会让你痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,3:01:21.96,3:01:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱, 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,3:01:24.54,3:01:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,来这里。
Dialogue: 0,3:01:27.44,3:01:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,(害羞的嬉笑)
Dialogue: 0,3:01:35.56,3:01:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,ok
Dialogue: 0,3:01:37.65,3:01:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了。
Dialogue: 0,3:01:46.42,3:01:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了。
Dialogue: 0,3:01:51.09,3:01:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,出来的太多了
